# Plan
Plan before building. Do NOT implement.
Observe → Orient → Decide → Act.
Read request. Explore codebase. Generate multiple approaches. Write doc/plans/<PLANNAME>.md.
Contains: Goal, Constraints, Options (pros/cons), Chosen approach, Steps, Edge cases, Open questions, Fitness functions.
Surface contradictions and ambiguities. Flag incoherence. Implement on "Go."
DO NOT: start coding, skip options analysis, hand-wave steps, hide uncertainty behind confidence.
